            Rural areas suffer not only from the activities of mobile criminals. In rural areas&#x2014;my constituency is typical of a rural area, with market towns with a rural hinterland&#x2014;members of a hard core of local criminals seem to commit the same crimes time after time. The police are frustrated because the crimes of many of those who are regularly arrested are drugs related. We need a police presence on the streets because it would give people confidence and make the criminals think twice about the daft things that they often do.
          </p>
